text: Akçay Dam is a dam in Turkey. It is on Akçay River which is a tributary of Sakarya River. It is situated in Gölpazarı ilçe (district) of Bilecik Province at close to Softalar village. It is a rockfill dam. The height of the dam is and the dam volume is . Its storage capacity is . Haberlar (news )page The dam has recently been completed.
